        public void onMapReady(com.google.android.gms.maps.GoogleMap googleMap)
        Manipulates the map once available. This callback is triggered when the map is ready to be used. This is where we can add markers or lines, add listeners or move the camera. In this case, we just add a marker near Sydney, Australia.
